Nollywood actress, Nnanji Charity has revealed how she escaped the request for s3x for the role by movie producers and directors. The pretty light-skinned actress said her journey to Nollywood was quite rough because s3x for the role was the order of the day. She, however, revealed how she was able to avoid such requests.   Alma Mata honours Comedian Bovi     I’m not afraid of giving love another chance –…     ‘Stefflon the best woman Burna Boy will ever…   “My journey into Nollywood has not been easy why because s3x for the role is the order of the day, once you are not ready to submit your body to either producer or director then you have no movie roles,” said Nnanji. On how she made her way to become a rising star without offering s3x, she said: “I was able to avoid those things because  I was capable of producing my movie.” Also speaking on the selection of movie roles, Nnanji said she would never act in a bedroom scene no matter how much money is involved.